c: 2
v: 89
t: "Yeroo kitaabni Rabbiin biraa ta’e kan waan isaanii wajjin jiru (Tawraatifi injiilin) dhugoomsu isaanitti dhufu, kan san dura akka warra kafaran irratti injifannoo argataniif [dhufaatii Nabi Muhammadiin SAW Rabbiin] kadhachaa turanii yeroo wanti isaan beekan isaanitti dhufu isatti kafaranKanaafuu abaarsi Rabbii kaafiroota irra haa jiraatu"